section.def:
Secretary means the Secretary for Home and Youth Affairs;
                (Amended L.N. 144 of
            2022)

subparagraph.content:
receive and consider such evidence as it considers relevant, whether or
                        not it would be admissible in a court of law, and require evidence to be
                        given on oath and either orally or in writing;

require the production of, admit or take into account any record,
                        statement or other document or any information or matter whether or not it
                        would be admissible in a court of law;

confirm, vary, reverse or revoke the decision appealed against or
                        substitute therefor such other decision or make such other order as it
                        thinks fit;
